{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some people thrown some things over-- some food, some bread pieces or things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then they're-- each time we thrown in a piece of bread, about 20 girls jumped on it in the dust, and they were fighting for it for 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So eventually the-- the bread become mixed up in the soil, and they just try to eat a little bit of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Fighting destroyed the whole bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Anyhow, eventually we got to our-- our destination, to our barrack, which was a standard Birkenau barrack, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was built to hold about maybe 150 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They put a thousand people in it, very tightly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And oh yeah, and so the usual procedure-- the-- the barrack commander had a very hard job, because he had to keep order over a thousand people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he was just himself and maybe had three or four attendants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So he had to hit people all the time with a heavy stick to-- to have some discipline, because I mean, a thousand people could easily have overwhelmed him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He was a fairly well-built German criminal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He had green triangle, which means he was a criminal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He was probably a murderer or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "A rapist, maybe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Anyhow, he kept hitting people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And he said anybody who has any jewelry on him or hidden away, or built into his shoes, into heels-- because that was a good place to hide diamonds-- hand-- hand it to me right now, because after one hour, we shall make a [INAUDIBLE] check of all shoes and everything.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If I find any jewelry on you, you're gonna be hanged up on that post.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So hanging up there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Lot of people hang up-- hung up there yesterday.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
